{"tid":1531431,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"再次警世：唔駛驚俾人拉，唯一要驚係驚打輸","createTime":"2019-09-02T08:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T15:23:37.000Z","uid":89974,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aac343c246c1eaa550d8ec1fb67a97930b76a467","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"想同個班仲潔身自愛連閘都唔敢跳既人講：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n警察而家已經係真真正正既軍政府，拉人係唔駛講道理<br />\n佢地已經係全港民眾既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵人</span></span><br />\n亦因為咁樣，大家係唔需要擔心俾人拉同俾人告<br />\n因為而家唔俾人拉，輸咗之後都係會俾人拉，只有贏咗先救到自己</span><br />\n<br />\n而且就算未贏，只要你條罪唔大，人夠多都係唔會入到你，例如<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>跳閘</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當然我唔係叫你而家去打劫金行，唔該用番良知去諗野<br />\n<br />\n總之唔好再拘泥於佢用咩罪告你，咩街坊送頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家警權就係大到點都搵到條罪charge你，打鳩你，我地先要企出嚟反對阿嘛</span></span><br />\n暴動？非法集結？藏有攻擊性武器？只要贏到你仲駛乜驚佢用咩嚟搞你，到時全民特赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正要避免既係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不可復原永久性損傷</span></span>，例如眼，腳，骨，呢啲無得100%復原先係真正既損耗。至於留唔留案底？驚乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而為咗避免俾人打，咁就記住點都要扮暈扮痛扮就嚟死，唔好俾狗咬你番差館<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者，你再潔身自愛，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">輸咗你都係等俾人告嫁咋</span></span>。今次輸咗的話23條過硬，仲記唔記得黨報成日話我地港獨啊？到時出過嚟既人全部入哂分裂國家罪係集中營見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTLDR：<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1.每日影一次自己全身相，保證無穿無爛<br />\n2.做任何野都可以勇敢多一步，唔駛驚俾人拉俾人告，而家法律暫時係廢架<br />\n3.集體行動，一俾人拉就暈低叫FA車你入醫院<br />\n4.唔小心入到狗局，咩都唔好講保障自己</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e2287e865a793d95a08446ee50c8162009757ab9","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"學生同理，唔駛驚大過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要人夠多，你係可以兇番班老師轉頭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d417bf8874310d7576898448dd427685ab3668","tid":1531431,"uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:19:59.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a35cd2bf49821f69f3e0e483551014de18261f","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家行前多一步，個責任就唔駛擺哂落前線到<br />\n佢亦都無可能拉哂2百萬人"},{"pid":"7fbe59b8f98c75eb6f40d6ad10a9aff843f1b73d","tid":1531431,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91398085fdf5c4d49ab3e00c958418b63137a35","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:21:19.000Z","msg":"誇張啲講句，2百萬個人一人一刀捅死某個人再鞭屍，都係告你唔入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ae823ce7693d0d79dc0472b740a405663c9dd1","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"諗下我地贏咗之後既香港係幾咁強大同美麗，<br />\n最起碼樓價一定唔會咁撚高先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母而家食串魚蛋都10蚊雞"},{"pid":"87ccb9679da3e24776327bc5ca262aa10a6066f6","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"今晚十點大家一齊大叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家</span></span>，班狗夠疆咪逐家逐戶拍門囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e139e96aa54479cd92ae4278c005099efa572f40","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"你有你告我，我有我做野<br />\n到時邊個輸邊個奶對家鞋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd63bd5e5376604ba934a91a5f73b1dc95b0bb0","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:24:51.000Z","msg":"單機十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787df88a97225b2d51380fb843e45ac33488275c","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"唔好再等天收啦，我地收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a7d81db3a8c704c9e3e104aa48f56c56909ad2","tid":1531431,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"勇武拉一個少一個"},{"pid":"d3827b04387115482ee6e21594d468fa1aab6a50","tid":1531431,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,